- Perform a rapid evaluation of the woman's general condition and then start DR. ABC protocol;
- D - Danger
- R - Response
- Airway
- Breathing
- Circulation

Evaluate the level of consciousness (AVPU; A- alertness, V-verbal response, P- pulse, UUnresponsive).

