- Persistent headache
- Visual disturbances-scotomas/blurring of vision
- Right upper quadrant pain
- Epigastric pain
- Intrauterine growth restriction of the fetus
- Oligohydramnios
- Oliguria less than 500 ml in 24 hours
- Pulmonary edema

