- Failed induction
- Uterine hyperstimulation
- Non reassuring fetal status
- Rupture of uterus

\section*{Failed induction}

\section*{Reassessment of maternal and fetal status}

The following are options for subsequent management:
- Another attempt to induce labour with a different method can be considered after discussion with the patient but it depends on indication of the induction of labor and expedite of delivery
- OR Caesarean delivery

