\section*{$\left.\right|^{\text {st }}$ week weight loss}

Term: I-2\% of birth weight per day, maximum 5-7\%. Regain birthweight by 7-10 days.

Preterm (LBW): weight loss $2-3 \%$ of birth weight per day, maximum $10-15 \%$. Regain birth weight by 10-14 days.

\section*{For all newborns:}
- First 7-14 days
